          <p>V</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </center>
  </div>
  <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:100px;">
    <center>
      <div class="circle_name circle_name-bongsa_time">
        <p>봉사 시간</p>
      </div>
      <div class="circle_name circle_name-d_day">
        <p>D-day</p>
      </div>
      <div class="circle_name circle_name-activ_region">
        <p>활동 지역</p>
      </div>
      <div class="circle_name circle_name-printable_doc">
        <p>인증서발급여부</p>
      </div>
    </center>
  </div>
</div>
